==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lanseh
<hw>Lan"seh</hw> <pr>(l⟦adot⟧n"s⟦asl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
small, yellow to whitish brown berrylike fruit of an East Indian tree
(<spn>Lansium domesticum</spn>). It has a fleshy pulp, with an agreeable
tart subacid taste.</def> <rj><au>Balfour.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lansah, lansa, lansat, lanset.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

